    "body": "### Feature already in Vim?\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/vim/vim/pull/3561\r\n\r\n### Feature description\r\n\r\nIn windows- when one opens a second and consecutive file, and Neovim is already open, open new files in new buffers.\r\n![PXL_20220804_204434442](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/36412717/182949169-3127f1bd-4095-49f6-890b-42139ce23ae8.jpg)\r\n",
